sub_title: Marketing Coordinator at ADJ Europe | Graphic Designer | Video Editor | Indep. Music Producer
summary:
Enterprising and driven man with an open and sociable personality, majoring in Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign, Premiere Pro and After Effects. Currently working as the European Marketing Coordinator at ADJ Lighting, in which several innovations have been initiated and accomplished. Specialized in successfully achieving effective and systematic professionalization of a brand.

Music = Passion

A music producer with over 2 decades of experience in electronic music (house/harder styles/techno), with over 100 songs released on various labels. Currently working mainly as a producer of his own songs and in collaboration with and for other artists/talents.

With a strong network of people with different disciplines, it is possible to get even the most impossible things done. Contact Danny for more info!
